---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-base-200">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Light Lane Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8">
        Effective Date: August 15, 2025 • Contact: <a
          href="mailto:support@lightlane.app"
          class="link link-primary">support@lightlane.app</a
        >
      </p>

      <p class="mb-8">
        This Privacy Policy describes how Light Lane ("Company," "we," "our," or
        "us") collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal data when you
        access, install, or use the Light Lane application, website, or any
        related services (collectively, the "Services").
      </p>
      <p class="mb-8">
        By using our Services, you acknowledge and agree to this Privacy Policy.
        If you do not agree, do not use our Services.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Scope &amp; Applicability</h2>
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy applies to all users of the Services, whether
            you have been invited to participate in our private beta or have
            obtained access through other means. Access to Light Lane without an
            official invitation is strictly prohibited and may lead to legal
            consequences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="font-medium mt-2">a. Information You Provide Directly</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 mb-4">
            <li>Name, email address, and contact information</li>
            <li>Account registration details</li>
            <li>
              Payment and billing information (processed through secure
              third-party providers; we do not store raw credit card data)
            </li>
            <li>
              Any content or data uploaded into the Light Lane application,
              including design files, project settings, and user preferences
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="font-medium">b. Information Collected Automatically</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>Device information (model, operating system, browser type)</li>
            <li>IP address and approximate geolocation</li>
            <li>Usage logs, crash reports, and performance data</li>
            <li>Date and time of access</li>
            <li>
              Interaction metrics (feature usage, time spent, click patterns)
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Purpose of Data Collection</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>Operating and maintaining the Services</li>
            <li>
              Improving product performance, stability, and user experience
            </li>
            <li>Providing customer support and responding to inquiries</li>
            <li>Processing transactions and enforcing payment terms</li>
            <li>Preventing unauthorized access and fraud</li>
            <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            4. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR Compliance)
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>
              Contractual necessity (to provide the Services you requested)
            </li>
            <li>
              Legitimate interests (e.g., preventing fraud, improving security)
            </li>
            <li>Consent (where required, such as for marketing emails)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the
            purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention
            period is required by law. Once data is no longer needed, it will be
            securely deleted or anonymized.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement industry-standard technical, administrative, and
            physical safeguards to protect your information. However, no system
            is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of
            your data.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Sharing of Information</h2>
          <p>We may share your data only in the following circumstances:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 mb-4">
            <li>
              With service providers (e.g., payment processors, analytics
              providers) under binding agreements to protect your data
            </li>
            <li>
              For legal compliance when required by law or governmental request
            </li>
            <li>
              In business transfers if we merge, sell, or restructure the
              Company
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            8. International Data Transfers
          </h2>
          <p>
            Your data may be stored and processed outside of your country of
            residence, including in jurisdictions that may not have the same
            data protection laws. By using the Services, you consent to such
            transfers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">9. Children’s Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            The Services are not directed to individuals under the age of 18. We
            do not knowingly collect data from children. If we become aware that
            we have collected personal data from a minor, we will delete it
            immediately.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">10. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 mb-4">
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
            <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
            <li>Data portability</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for certain processing activities</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise these rights, contact <a
              href="mailto:support@lightlane.app"
              class="link">support@lightlane.app</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            11. Beta &amp; Invite-Only Disclaimer
          </h2>
          <p>
            Light Lane is currently in a private beta phase and invite-only. Any
            access obtained without official invitation is strictly prohibited.
            Unauthorized use, distribution, or access to the software will be
            treated as a violation of this Privacy Policy, our Terms, and
            applicable laws.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">12. No Refund Policy</h2>
          <p>
            All purchases are final and non-refundable. By using the Services
            and completing any payment, you agree to this policy.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">13. Changes to this Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Updates will be
            posted on our website and become effective upon posting. Continued
            use of the Services after changes are made constitutes your
            acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">14. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please
            contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <strong>Light Lane Support</strong><br />Email: <a
              href="mailto:support@lightlane.app"
              class="link">support@lightlane.app</a
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
